Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂当鬼了 海蒂当鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
