Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就开始做站起来的练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们 开饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美味的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.45,0:22:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉 我会等待你的好消息的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 我会努力的
